makePCA_ageonly = function(df, age, PCx, PCy, title){
  PCA = prcomp(t(df), scale = FALSE)
  percentVar = round(100*PCA$sdev^2/sum(PCA$sdev^2),1)
  sd_ratio = sqrt(percentVar[2] / percentVar[1])
  dataGG = data.frame(PCx = PCA$x[,PCx], 
                      PCy = PCA$x[,PCy],
                      Sample = colnames(df),
                      Age = age)
  ggplot(dataGG, aes(PCx, PCy)) +
    geom_point(aes(colour = Age), size = 3) +
    guides(size = FALSE, color = guide_legend(override.aes = list(size=4)))+
    ggtitle(title) +
    scale_color_manual(values=c(child="#5D3C91", infant="#45989B", neonate ="#EFB931"))+
    xlab(paste0("PC",PCx, ", VarExp: ", percentVar[PCx], "%")) +
    ylab(paste0("PC",PCy, ", VarExp: ", percentVar[PCy], "%")) +
    theme(plot.title = element_text(hjust = 0.5),
          panel.grid.major = element_blank(),
          panel.grid.minor = element_blank(),
          panel.background = element_rect(fill = "white", colour = "white", size = 0.5, linetype = "solid"),
          axis.text.x = element_text(color = "black", size = 12),
          axis.text.y = element_text(color = "black", size = 12),
          axis.title.x = element_text(color="black", size=14),
          axis.title.y = element_text(color="black", size=14),
          legend.key = element_blank()) +
    coord_fixed(ratio = sd_ratio) +
    theme(aspect.ratio=1) +
    geom_hline(yintercept=0, color = "gray45", size=0.5) +
    geom_vline(xintercept=0, color = "gray45", size=0.5)}

Volcano Plot

library(EnhancedVolcano)
makevp = function(results, firstcolor, secondcolor) {
  keyvals = ifelse((results$logFC < -1 & results$P.Value<0.05), secondcolor, ifelse((results$logFC > 1 & results$P.Value<0.05), firstcolor,'black'))
  keyvals[is.na(keyvals)] <- 'black'
  names(keyvals)[keyvals == firstcolor] <- 'first'
  names(keyvals)[keyvals == 'black'] <- 'mid'
  names(keyvals)[keyvals == secondcolor] <- 'second'
  EnhancedVolcano(results,
                lab = NA,
                x = 'logFC',
                y = 'P.Value',
                pCutoff = 0.05,
                FCcutoff = 1.0,
                title = "",
                subtitle = "lncRNA seq",
                legendPosition = 'none',
                legendLabSize = 1,
                colAlpha = 1,
                gridlines.major = FALSE,
                gridlines.minor = FALSE,
                colCustom = keyvals,
                ylim = c(0,7),
                legendIconSize = 3)}
